<textEffects>(And so, like a ballad, the trial flowed on and on... until it came to the end. Thanks to the trial... ..."<span style="color:#E16935">The Guitar's Serenade</textEffects>" was a huge hit. Prosecutor Gavin's even more dazzling to look at now. But... there's something I want to say to that guy. Next time you write a ballad...)</span>
